#   PRESENT:  joda-time:joda-time:2.10.8  (via aws-lambda-java-events)
#   PRESENT:  commons-codec               (via secretsmanager -> apache-client)
#   ABSENT:   spring-webmvc, guava        (belong to payments-api only)
